content: That's great, thanks for the party favor ideas! I think I'll go with the Tiara or Crown and the Princess Stickers or Tattoos. They seem like something the kids will really enjoy. By the way, I've been thinking about my shopping list and I realized I need to pick up some more art supplies. I got my niece a nice set of art supplies as a gift, but I want to make sure I have some extras on hand for the art station at the party. Do you have any suggestions for art supplies that kids around the age of 5 usually enjoy?
